### Get all items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get item by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/5 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Post item
POST http://localhost:5000/api/items HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": "Tomato",
  "amount": "",
  "price": "",
  "shop": "",
  "measure": "",
  "currency": ""
}

### Put item
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/items HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 5,
  "product": "Laptop",
  "amount": "1",
  "price": "850.00",
  "shop": "Comfy",
  "measure": "unit",
  "currency": "USD"
}

### Delete item
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/items/5 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json